<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
    <style type="text/css">
      a, p {
        font-family: Avenir, sans-serif;
        font-size: 15px;
      }

      a {
        color: #000cac;
        text-decoration:none;
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
  <div style="background-color:#fbfbfb">
    <div style="border-bottom:2px solid #eeeeee;background-color:#ffffff">
      <table cellspacing="0" align="center" width="600" cellpadding="0"><tbody>
        <tr>
          <td valign="middle" width="40" height="50">
            <%= link_to root_path, :target => "_blank" do %>
              <%= image_tag attachments['logo.png'].url %>
            <% end %>
          </td>
          <td align="right">
            <%= link_to "Log In", new_user_session_path, :target => "_blank" %>
          </td>
        </tr>
      </tbody></table>
    </div>

    <table align="center" width="600" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0"><tbody>
      <tr><td height="30">&nbsp;</td></tr>
      <tr>
        <td valign="top">
          <%= image_tag attachments['header.jpg'].url, :class => "header" %>
          <table style="border:1px solid #eee;" bgcolor="#ffffff" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" align="center" width="600"><tbody>
            <tr>
              <td>
                <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" align="center" width="550"><tbody>
                  <tr><td valign="top" colspan="2" height="30">&nbsp;</td></tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td width="30">&nbsp;</td>
                    <td valign="top" colspan="2">

<p>Hey <%= @user.first_name %>,</p>

<p>This is just a note to let you know that you have successfully signed up for Tipster! I know this is a big moment, and you might be feeling a bit overwhelmed. Don't worry, I'm emotional about it too.</p>

<p>If you need an idea where to start, try adding the <a href="https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/tipster/kcaggdadonedjneipfkphbianejifnep">Chrome extension</a>. It's the fastest way to share cool stuff with your friends. (Oh, and you'll also need some friends.)</p>

<p>Already got all that? Then you're all set! You'll be a celebrated internet content maven in no time.</p>

<p>If you ever have any questions or comments, or just want to say hi, feel free to email me directly at <a href="mailto:garrett@tipster.to">garrett@tipster.to</a> and I'll get right back to you.</p>

<p>Thanks for trying Tipster, I hope you enjoy it.</p>

<p>Cheers,</p>

<p>Garrett</p>

                    </td>
                    <td width="30">&nbsp;</td>
                  </tr>
       
                  <tr>
                    <td valign="top" height="30" style="height:30px">&nbsp;</td>
                  </tr>
                </tbody></table>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </tbody></table>
          <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" align="center" width="540"><tbody>
            <tr>
              <td height="20">&nbsp;</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>
                <p style="font-size:9pt;color:#8b959e;text-decoration:none;text-align:center">
                  You're receiving this because you signed up for a Tipster account with this email.<br>Wasn't you? <a href="mailto:garrett@tipster.to">Let me know</a>.               
                </p>
                <p style="font-size:9pt;color:#8b959e;text-decoration:none;text-align:center">
                  Want to get rid of these emails? <a href="#" target="_blank">Manage your email preferences</a>.
                </p>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </tbody></table>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td height="50">&nbsp;</td>
      </tr>
    </tbody></table>
  </div>
  </body>
</html>